{"tid":1325054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傳媒良心】RTHK 視點31 重整714沙田事發始末","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:13:57.000Z","uid":79382,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"637494ccfcfe342a91d76146cc521ff248bcb76d","tid":1325054,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1774538779359279?s=711566308&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F371653272981177%2Fposts%2F1774538779359279%3Fs%3D711566308%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a0f8a8a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1774538779359279?s=711566308&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n地圖展示警狗當晚四面包抄，<br />\n示威者被迫退入新城市廣場，<br />\n再喺商場入面俾狗窮追猛打，<br />\n成件事講解得好清晰......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但同時要屌撚死仆街CCTVB！</strong></span></span><br />\n人哋RTHK政府部門都未撚驚過，<br />\n見到乜嘢就報道乜嘢，<br />\n你間私人企業就日撚日都好似驚奶唔切鞋底咁，<br />\n永遠記者日頭採訪到嘅嘢，<br />\n俾你班共狗改撚到不似人形，<br />\n手握大氣電波，坐擁公共資源，日日出賣香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23217fff1fd1cd875c661723f80c8d1b51c9d0f8","tid":1325054,"uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"推畀更多人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然民意冇明顯逆轉，<br />\n同埋民意亦未必係最重要，<br />\n但既然有傳媒已經幫手整咗，<br />\n就盡力廣傳開去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ad5c6e5d5c2ccf08ea3c60c859ff70f26e1c4b","tid":1325054,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}